    "en": {
      "title": "Health unions strike",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Several unions in the health sector have announced that they will join the union action tomorrow (29) and the next day, Thursday (30).",
        "Eight unions of the auxiliary health union will begin union action in the next two days.",
        "Public health inspectors (PHIs), family planning officers, laboratory technicians and epidemiologists are part of the union representatives.",
        "The health auxiliary health union will go on strike in connection with the fuel shortage in the country."
      ],
